A **professional** 2D/2.5D game engine built with Python and Pygame. VoidRay provides the core infrastructure and tools needed to build any type of game, while giving developers complete control over their game logic and mechanics.

---

## ğŸš€ Engine Features (v3)

### ğŸ¯ **Core Engine Systems**
- **ğŸ§© ECS Architecture**: Modern Entity-Component-System for flexible game objects
- **âš¡ Advanced Physics**: Collision detection, rigidbodies, and spatial partitioning with quadtree optimization
- **ğŸ® Multi-Input Support**: Keyboard, mouse, gamepad with frame-perfect detection
- **ğŸµ Spatial Audio**: 3D positioned audio with distance attenuation and effects
- **ğŸ“¦ Asset Streaming**: Efficient loading, caching, and resource streaming
- **ğŸ¨ Advanced Renderer**: 2.5D graphics pipeline with depth sorting and post-processing
- **ğŸ”§ Debug Tools**: Performance monitoring, profiler, and visual debugging overlay
- **ğŸ’¾ Save System**: JSON and binary save/load with integrity checking

### ğŸ—ï¸ **What You Build**
VoidRay gives you the foundation - **you create the game**:
- **Game Logic**: Your gameplay mechanics, rules, and systems
